  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nIn a discussion w @dapplion:\r\n> Oh, the node is running minimal, and the validator is running mainnet\r\n\r\nWe'd like to prevent that scenario from happening.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nAdd a check in the validator to ensure that the validator is connecting to a beacon node w the same configuration.\r\nEg: fetch from the `config.getSpec` endpoint and compare against local values. Throw if the beacon node isn't configured the same as the validator.\r\n",
